STATE
v.
Kunta K. WINDLEY. No. 259P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. September 26, 2005.

Kunta Kinte Windley, Pro Se, Charlesena E. Walker, Assistant Appellate Defender.

Thomas J. Keith, District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 23rd day of September 2005 by Attorney General for Temporary Stay:

"Motion Allowed pending determination of the State's petition for discretionary review *681by order of the Court in conference this the 26th day of September 2005."
